VALUES (376, 'Rubius X', 3, 3, 2022, '76 min', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/k6KAAVebtdVb0FRU2PWqYLnhgRA.jpg', 'Hace ya 10 anos del primer video publicado por el Rubius en YouTube. Con motivo de esta celebracion llega "Rubius X", el documental sobre uno de los creadores de contenido espanoles mas reconocidos. Conoceremos la historia de la revolucion que causo el nacimiento de YouTube con una de las figuras pioneras en el sector y el influencer mas popular en Espana e Hispanoamerica con mas de 40 millones de seguidores.', 8.6, '2026-06-10');
VALUES (377, 'Lil Peep: Everybody''s Everything', 3, 3, 2019, '115 min', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wbMkjkNX8VylPVLmQ2Dp6i5iayY.jpg', 'Este intimo retrato muestra el ascenso del artista Lil Peep, cuya musica que fusiona distintos generos atrajo a una gran cantidad de seguidores y definio su vida.', 8.5, '2026-06-11');
VALUES (378, 'Realtime', 3, 3, 2007, 'Duracion Desconocida', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jKpu0FmGSFTO1QMt2ROsO3YsCWa.jpg', 'Six months of skiing action. Lots of snow. Weeks of rain. Sun. Clouds. Fog. Blue Skies. Unforgiving concrete. Untracked landings. Low Pressure. High fives. Triple kinks. Double grabs. Too much speed. Not enough gas. Underrotated. Overtweaked. A chronological portrayal of the trials, tribulations, and triumphs of the ''06-''07 exactly as it happened. Level 1 brings you, ''REALTIME.''  Directed by award-winning filmmaker Josh Berman and shot in HD across the globe, Realtime captures the season as it unfolds for a crew of the biggest names and best up and coming talent in skiing. In a winter quite unlike any other to date, Level 1 throws down a fresh new format with their trademark style, and nothing short of the best cinematography in action sports filmmaking.', 0.0, '2026-06-12');
VALUES (379, 'First Invasion: The War of 1812', 3, 3, 2004, '46 min', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/orFeMZNIF1e08RPc9MNhw3UOfSX.jpg', 'First Invasion: The War of 1812, a History Channel documentary that first aired in 2004, portrays a young United States of America "on the brink of annihilation" as it battles the largest and most powerful empire on earth. Critics say the documentary is far too pro-American, and that it ignores or downplays crucial elements of the War of 1812. Others praise First Invasion for its compelling presentation of a far too neglected period of history.', 0.0, '2026-06-13');
